Poussi, Poussy ma ọ bụ Boussy (Arabic) ezigbo aha Safenaz Moustafa Adry (amụrụ na 26 Nọvemba 1953) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri a mụrụ na Cairo.
A mụrụ Poussi na Shoubra, Cairo nye nne na nna Ijipt
Nne nne ya bụ onye si n'agbụrụ ndị Turkey.

Ọ lụrụ onye Egypt a ma ama na-eme ihe nkiri Nour El Sherief na 1972 ma mụọ ụmụ nwanyị abụọ, otu n'ime ha bụkwa onye na-eme ihe nkiri ma pụta n'ọtụtụ usoro telivishọn n'akụkụ nna ya mana ọ gara n'ihu n'otu ọrụ ahụ
Ya na Nour El Sherief gbara alụkwaghịm na 2006 wee lụọ di ọzọ na 2015.
